#: .\modinfo.json
msgid "Nimian Manufacture Guns"
msgstr "尼米安製造槍械"

#. ~ Description for Nimian Manufacture Guns
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Adds a new set of guns, light and accurate, as well as some other toys."
msgstr "新增一套輕便精準的槍械，以及其他一些玩具。"

#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid "32mm concussive"
msgid_plural "32mm concussive"
msgstr[0] "32毫米震盪彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '32mm concussive', 'str_pl': '32mm concussive'}
#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid "A 32mm grenade with a concussive explosion load."
msgstr "一枚裝載震盪爆炸裝藥的32毫米榴彈。"

#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid "32mm frag"
msgid_plural "32mm frag"
msgstr[0] "32毫米破片彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '32mm frag', 'str_pl': '32mm frag'}
#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A 32mm grenade with a small explosive load and a high number of damaging "
"fragments."
msgstr "一枚裝載少量炸藥和大量傷害性破片的32毫米榴彈。"

#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid "32mm incendiary"
msgid_plural "32mm incendiary"
msgstr[0] "32毫米燃燒彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '32mm incendiary', 'str_pl': '32mm incendiary'}
#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A 32mm grenade with a small napalm load, designed to create a burst of "
"flame."
msgstr "一枚裝載少量凝固汽油的32毫米榴彈，旨在製造一陣火焰。"

#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid "32mm teargas"
msgid_plural "32mm teargas"
msgstr[0] "32毫米催淚彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '32mm teargas', 'str_pl': '32mm teargas'}
#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A 32mm grenade with a teargas load.  It will burst in a cloud of highly "
"incapacitating gas."
msgstr "一枚裝載催淚瓦斯的32毫米榴彈。它將在高致殘性氣體雲中爆炸。"

#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid "32mm smoke cover"
msgid_plural "32mm smoke cover"
msgstr[0] "32毫米煙霧掩護彈"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '32mm smoke cover', 'str_pl': '32mm smoke cover'}
#: .\nm_ammo.json
msgid ""
"A 32mm grenade with a smoke load.  It will burst in a cloud of harmless gas,"
" and will also leave a streak of smoke cover in its wake."
msgstr "一枚裝載煙霧劑的32毫米榴彈。它將在無害氣體雲中爆炸，並在其軌跡上留下一道煙霧掩護。"

