msgid "Nimian's Manufacture Hunter Pack"
msgid_plural "Nimian's Manufacture Hunter Packs"
msgstr[0] "尼米安製造獵人套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Nimian's Manufacture Hunter Pack", 'str_pl':
#. "Nimian's Manufacture Hunter Packs"}
#: .\nm_misc.json
msgid ""
"Heavy case which contains NM150 sniper rifle, some ammo for it, maintenance "
"kit (sadly, without batteries), and Last Hope pistol-shotgun as a... free "
"gift? The label says it's preferred choice for hunters."
msgstr ""
"重型箱子，內含NM150狙擊步槍、配套彈藥、維護工具包（可惜沒有電池），以及一把“最後希望”手槍式霰彈槍作為……免費贈品？標籤上寫著這是獵人的首選。"

#: .\nm_misc.json
msgid "Nimian's Manufacture Improved Flaregun Pack"
msgid_plural "Nimian's Manufacture Improved Flaregun Pack"
msgstr[0] "尼米安製造改進型信號槍套裝"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Nimian's Manufacture Improved Flaregun Pack",
#. 'str_pl': "Nimian's Manufacture Improved Flaregun Pack"}
#: .\nm_misc.json
msgid ""
"Heavy case which contains NM456, some flares for it and maintenance kit "
"(sadly, without batteries)."
msgstr "重型箱子，內含NM456、配套信號彈和維護工具包（可惜沒有電池）。"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM377 12g"
msgid_plural "NM377s 12g"
msgstr[0] "NM377 12號口徑"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture pistol, also nicknamed 'Last Hope'. Essentially a "
"factory-made one-shot short shotgun, more accurate than home-made ones, but "
"still only doing well in close-range. Developed in a few months before "
"cataclysm to earn money on common people's paranoia, it did well in that."
msgstr ""
"尼米安製造的手槍，綽號“最後希望”。本質上是一把工廠製造的單發短霰彈槍，比自制型號更精準，但仍只適合近距離使用。在大災變前幾個月為利用民眾的恐慌心理賺錢而開發，效果顯著。"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM379 9mm"
msgid_plural "NM377s 9mm"
msgstr[0] "NM379 9毫米"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture pistol, a small, light and cheap weapon designed for "
"self-defense. Holds 2 rounds, and every single one has to be inserted "
"manually, making reload difficult."
msgstr "尼米安製造的手槍，一種為自衛設計的小型、輕量且廉價的武器。可容納2發子彈，每發都需手動裝填，使得重新裝彈困難。"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM338"
msgid_plural "NM338s"
msgstr[0] "NM338"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture laser pistol, brings the power of laser to a common "
"man. Uses charged battery packs, unlike most energy weapons out there."
msgstr "尼米安製造的激光手槍，將激光的力量帶給普通人。與大多數能量武器不同，它使用充電電池包。"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid "NM392 7x30mm"
msgid_plural "NM392s 7x30mm"
msgstr[0] "NM392 7x30毫米"

#: .\nm_weapons_cheap.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture six-shot revolver chambered for 7x30mm, made with low "
"cost and durability in mind."
msgstr "尼米安製造的六發左輪手槍，使用7x30毫米彈藥，設計注重低成本和耐用性。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM103 9mm"
msgid_plural "NM103s 9mm"
msgstr[0] "NM103 9毫米"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"First gun ever to be developed by Nimian's Manufacture, this lightweight "
"rifle is very accurate and durable, but clip size is very small as a result."
msgstr "尼米安製造公司開發的第一把槍，這種輕量步槍非常精準耐用，但因此彈匣容量很小。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM302 .50"
msgid_plural "NM302s .50"
msgstr[0] "NM302 .50口徑"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"This pistol, developed by Nimian's Manufacture in around 2038, employs "
"several creative ideas and lots of superalloy to make firing .50 BMG round "
"in a pistol worthwhile."
msgstr "這把由尼米安製造公司約在2038年開發的手槍，採用了幾項創意設計和大量超級合金，使得在手槍中發射.50 BMG子彈變得有價值。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM322 .22"
msgid_plural "NM322s .22"
msgstr[0] "NM322 .22口徑"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture .22 pistol. Small size of the round actually allowed "
"engineers to make the pistol hold more than 4 rounds, while also adding a "
"burst-fire mode."
msgstr "尼米安製造的.22口徑手槍。子彈的小尺寸實際上讓工程師能夠使手槍容納超過4發子彈，同時還增加了連發模式。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "semi auto"
msgstr "半自動"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "burst"
msgstr "連發"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM380 .45"
msgid_plural "NM380s .45"
msgstr[0] "NM380 .45口徑"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture .45 pistol. Advertised as 'sniper pistol', this little "
"beauty has anything a good marksman needs: an built-in scope, a stock that "
"can also be used as holster and incredible accuracy to boot. Holds only 4 "
"rounds though."
msgstr ""
"尼米安製造的.45口徑手槍。廣告宣傳為“狙擊手槍”，這個小美人擁有優秀射手所需的一切：內置瞄準鏡、可兼作槍套的槍托，以及驚人的精準度。但只能容納4發子彈。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM380 7x30mm"
msgid_plural "NM380s 7x30mm"
msgstr[0] "NM380 7x30毫米"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 7x30mm pistol, copy of the .45 pistol that was adapted "
"to use Nimian own ammunition. Advertised as 'sniper pistol', this little "
"beauty has anything a good marksman needs: an built-in scope, a stock that "
"can also be used as holster and incredible accuracy to boot. Holds 6 rounds."
" Best to use with match rounds."
msgstr ""
"尼米安製造的7x30毫米手槍，是.45口徑手槍的改型，適配尼米安自家彈藥。廣告宣傳為“狙擊手槍”，這個小美人擁有優秀射手所需的一切：內置瞄準鏡、可兼作槍套的槍托，以及驚人的精準度。可容納6發子彈。最好配合比賽級彈藥使用。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM323 5.56x45mm"
msgid_plural "NM323s 5.56x45mm"
msgstr[0] "NM323 5.56x45mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture pistol, chambered for 5.56x45mm ammo. It's still more "
"accurate than most guns out there, and still lightweight, but light weight "
"still makes it hard to control recoil, and it only holds 3 bullets."
msgstr "尼米安製造的手槍，使用5.56x45mm彈藥。它仍然比大多數槍支更精準，且重量輕，但輕量化也使其難以控制後坐力，且僅能裝填3發子彈。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM333"
msgid_plural "NM333s"
msgstr[0] "NM333"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture laser pistol, draws power from integrated plutonium "
"cell, so it can fire about 5.5 million times before discharging. The beam is"
" very weak though."
msgstr "尼米安製造的激光手槍，從內置鈈電池獲取能量，因此可發射約550萬次才耗盡。不過光束非常微弱。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM808 9mm"
msgid_plural "NM808s 9mm"
msgstr[0] "NM808 9mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 9mm submachine gun, pretty light for its size due to "
"superalloy, and rather damaging. Still has rather small clip, though this "
"one is big compared to other Nimian weapons."
msgstr "尼米安製造的9mm衝鋒槍，因採用超級合金，尺寸雖大卻相當輕便，且威力不俗。彈匣容量仍較小，但相比其他尼米安武器已算較大。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "auto"
msgstr "自動"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM808-S 9mm"
msgid_plural "NM808-Ss 9mm"
msgstr[0] "NM808-S 9mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 9mm submachine gun, this extremely rare variant is made"
" for the extremely rich people who can afford it. It has superalloy almost "
"everywhere, extensively modified and tuned extremely well."
msgstr "尼米安製造的9mm衝鋒槍，這款極為稀有的變種專為極富人群打造，幾乎全身採用超級合金，經過大量改裝與精細調校。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM104 9mm"
msgid_plural "NM104s 9mm"
msgstr[0] "NM104 9mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 9mm rifle, slightly heavier than NM103 but is more "
"accurate and can contain more ammunition."
msgstr "尼米安製造的9mm步槍，比NM103稍重，但更精準且能容納更多彈藥。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM220"
msgid_plural "NM220"
msgstr[0] "NM220"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture light shotgun, one of the not-so-succesful designs "
"since improved accuracy isn't very important for shotguns. Holds 3 rounds."
msgstr "尼米安製造的輕型霰彈槍，因提升精準度對霰彈槍並不重要，屬於不太成功的設計之一。可裝填3發彈藥。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM310 7x30mm"
msgid_plural "NM310s 7x30mm"
msgstr[0] "NM310 7x30mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "Nimian's Manufacture 7x30mm pistol, lightweight, accurate and durable."
msgstr "尼米安製造的7x30mm手槍，輕量、精準且耐用。"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid "NM810 7x30mm"
msgid_plural "NM810s 7x30mm"
msgstr[0] "NM810 7x30mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_civvie.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 7x30mm submachine gun, lightweight, accurate and "
"durable."
msgstr "尼米安製造的7x30mm衝鋒槍，輕量、精準且耐用。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM112 5.56x45mm"
msgid_plural "NM112s 5.56x45mm"
msgstr[0] "NM112 5.56x45mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 5.56x45mm marksman rifle, developed with accuracy in "
"mind, lightweight and decent. Overall a good weapon, but has a small clip."
msgstr "尼米安製造的5.56x45mm精確射手步槍，專為精準度設計，輕量且性能尚可。總體是款好武器，但彈匣容量小。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM113 5.56x45mm"
msgid_plural "NM113s 5.56x45mm"
msgstr[0] "NM113 5.56x45mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 5.56x45mm battle rifle, that weapon was designed for "
"military and as such, is heavier than most Nimian weapons but has a not-"
"THAT-small clip, and can fire in 3-shot bursts."
msgstr "尼米安製造的5.56x45mm戰鬥步槍，專為軍事用途設計，因此比大多數尼米安武器更重，但彈匣容量不算太小，且可進行3發點射。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM185"
msgid_plural "NM185s"
msgstr[0] "NM185"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture laser rifle, designed for military as UPS-independent "
"laser weapon. Instead, it uses charged battery packs to shoot. 7 shots per "
"reload."
msgstr "尼米安製造的激光步槍，作為獨立於UPS的激光武器為軍事設計。它使用充電電池包射擊，每次裝填可發射7次。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM192"
msgid_plural "NM192s"
msgstr[0] "NM192"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture heavy laser rifle, designed for military as laser anti-"
"materiel rifle, whatever that means. Rumours are that it was accepted only "
"because laser caused certain... effects on whatever was targeted. Works by "
"draining power from overcharged battery packs. Can hold 2."
msgstr ""
"尼米安製造的重型激光步槍，作為激光反器材步槍為軍事設計，無論這意味著什麼。傳聞稱其被接受僅因激光對目標能產生某種...效果。通過消耗過充電池包的能量運作，可容納2個電池包。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM150 .30-06"
msgid_plural "NM150s .30-06"
msgstr[0] "NM150 .30-06"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture .30-06 sniper rifle, holds only two rounds, but can and"
" will fire them very accurately. Has an built-in scope."
msgstr "尼米安製造的.30-06狙擊步槍，僅能裝填兩發子彈，但可極其精準地發射。配有內置瞄準鏡。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM221"
msgid_plural "NM221"
msgstr[0] "NM221"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture heavy shotgun, holds 5 shotgun shells and is able to "
"fire them all in one quick burst"
msgstr "尼米安製造的重型霰彈槍，可裝填5發霰彈，並能一次性快速齊射。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM456 32mm"
msgid_plural "NM456 32mm"
msgstr[0] "NM456 32mm"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture 'flaregun', as they call it, actually looks like an "
"grenade launcher, with a stock and iron sights to aim your 32mm 'flares'."
msgstr "尼米安製造的'信號槍'，如其名，實際外觀類似榴彈發射器，配有槍托和機械瞄具，用於瞄準32mm'信號彈'。"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid "NM100 25mm"
msgid_plural "NM100s 25mm"
msgstr[0] "NM100 25毫米"

#: .\nm_weapons_military.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture anti-materiel rifle. Presented for military as a "
"replacement for older anti-materiel rifles, this heavy weapon fires powerful"
" 25mm rounds. Effective against pretty much everything a survivor might "
"encounter, but has to be reloaded after each shot, and ammo is rare."
msgstr ""
"尼米安製造的反器材步槍。作為舊式反器材步槍的替代品向軍方推出，這款重型武器發射威力強大的25毫米彈藥。對倖存者可能遇到的幾乎所有目標都有效，但每次射擊後需重新裝填，且彈藥稀有。"

#: .\nm_weapons_proto.json
msgid "NMT01"
msgid_plural "NMT01s"
msgstr[0] "NMT01"

#: .\nm_weapons_proto.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture handheld tesla cannon. Rumours are that this weapon was"
" developed in Soviet Union back then, and that Nimian paid a lot for the "
"specifications of this magnificent weapon. This weapon is extremely "
"damaging, but requires a lot of power to fire."
msgstr "尼米安製造的手持特斯拉炮。傳聞此武器早年於蘇聯開發，尼米安為這款卓越武器的規格支付了鉅額費用。此武器傷害極高，但發射需要大量能量。"

#: .\nm_weapons_proto.json
msgid "NMT01 mk. 2"
msgid_plural "NMT01s mk. 2"
msgstr[0] "NMT01 改進型 2"

#: .\nm_weapons_proto.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture handheld tesla cannon. Rumours are that this weapon was"
" developed in Soviet Union back then, and that Nimian paid a lot for the "
"specifications of this magnificent weapon. This weapon is extremely "
"damaging, but requires a lot of power to fire. The mark 2 is even more "
"damaging, and lightning can jump between targets, but it'll drain through "
"charges even faster."
msgstr ""
"尼米安製造的手持特斯拉炮。傳聞此武器早年於蘇聯開發，尼米安為這款卓越武器的規格支付了鉅額費用。此武器傷害極高，但發射需要大量能量。改進型2的傷害更高，且閃電可在目標間跳躍，但會更快耗盡充能。"

#: .\nm_weapons_proto.json
msgid "NM199 10x62mm"
msgid_plural "NM199s 10x62mm"
msgstr[0] "NM199 10x62毫米"

#: .\nm_weapons_proto.json
msgid ""
"Nimian's Manufacture prototype sniper rifle, firing powerful 10x62mm "
"caseless rounds. Made to be as quiet as possible, and also has all that "
"high-tech stuff to reduce weight, recoil and make the gun easy to handle. "
"Holds 3 rounds."
msgstr ""
"尼米安製造的原型狙擊步槍，發射威力強大的10x62毫米無殼彈。設計力求儘可能安靜，並採用高科技材料減輕重量和後坐力，使槍支易於操控。可裝填3發彈藥。"
